overview.overview: Secure, cloud-native, scalable, self-hosted, open-core document sharing and collaboration without putting your data at risk.

childMarkdownRemark.html: Pydio Cells is an open-source file synchronization and sharing platform for Windows, macOS, and Linux. It provides a simple and intuitive interface with rich functionality for easy file management and collaboration. Pydio Cells supports multiple storage backends and access protocols, such as FTP, SFTP, SMB, etc., facilitating data storage and management. Additionally, it features version control and permission management, allowing easy tracking of file changes and restricting access permissions. Overall, Pydio Cells is a powerful and easy-to-use file synchronization and sharing tool suitable for enterprises and teams of all sizes.
